 <strong>  COMMENT </strong>
      
      <br>  <br>

Good Job Nana Dashyan. Yours was the best article whereas others were still polarized by the inherent hatrad stating words like Turks as enemy, Azerbaijan loosing the war, etc. May you live long to witness that peace. 	  
<br> <strong>Concerned person | 05.06.2008 </strong>	  

